**Key exam concept — explicit criteria:** Notice each tool description says
"Flag ONLY" and "Do NOT flag". This prevents each subagent from drifting into
the other agents' territory. Vague instructions like "assess the writing quality"
would cause each agent to evaluate everything, producing contradictory scores.

